text.__SUMMARY__: Pinus yunnanensis, the Yunnan pine, is a species of conifer in the family Pinaceae. It is found in the Chinese provinces of Yunnan, Sichuan, Guizhou, and Guangxi.
text.References: Conifer Specialist Group 1998.  Pinus yunnanensis.   2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.   Downloaded on 10 July 2007.
